## Prerequisites

- .NET 8.0 SDK or later

## Installation

```bash
# Restore dependencies
dotnet restore

# Build project
dotnet build

# Install Playwright browsers
pwsh bin/Debug/net8.0/playwright.ps1 install
```

## Running Tests

```bash
# Run all tests
dotnet test

# Run tests with specific environment
TEST_ENV=qa dotnet test

# Run tests in headed mode
HEADLESS=false dotnet test

# Run tests with specific browser
BROWSER=firefox dotnet test
```

## Environment Configuration

Update test data in:
- `Data/dev.json` - Development environment
- `Data/qa.json` - QA environment

Set environment with `TEST_ENV=qa`

## Page Objects

All page objects extend `BasePage` and are located in `Pages/`:
- `LoginPage.cs` - Login page interactions
- `HomePage.cs` - Home page interactions

